 level="4"><display>(C)</display>Native American Legislative Liaison Committee, created in Section <xref depth="3" refnumber="36-22-1" start="0">36-22-1</xref>; <ln numlevel="1" lineno="119" slineno="2-48"/>and</subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-33" dnum="ii-o" numlevel="1" lineno="120" slineno="2-49" level="3"><display>(ii)</display>that:<subsection ssid="1-null-34" dnum="A-o" numlevel="1" lineno="121" slineno="2-50" level="4"><display>(A)</display>identifies the source and amount of the revenue received by the fund;</subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-35" dnum="B-o" numlevel="1" lineno="122" slineno="2-51" level="4"><display>(B)</display>identifies the recipient, purpose, and amount of the expenditures from the fund;</subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-36" dnum="C-o" numlevel="1" lineno="123" slineno="2-52" level="4"><display>(C)</display>identifies <amendoutstart style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="erase" pairid="115" groupid="113" style="2" owner="admin" level="1" deltag="both">specifically each of the fund's investments and the actual return and <ln numlevel="1" lineno="124" slineno="2-53"/>the rate of return from each investment</amend><amendoutend style="2"/><amend anum="0" ea="amend" pairid="113" groupid="111" style="1" owner="admin" level="1" amendtag="both" space="true">investment categories and the rate of <ln numlevel="1" lineno="125" slineno="2-54"/>return of each category of investment</amend>; and</subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-37" dnum="D-o" numlevel="1" lineno="126" slineno="2-55" level="4"><display>(D)</display>recommends any necessary statutory changes to improve administration of the <ln numlevel="1" lineno="127" slineno="2-56"/>fund or to protect the state from liability as trustee;</subsection></subsection></subsection><subsection ssid="1-null-38" dnum="l-o" numlevel="1" lineno="128" slineno="2-57" level="2"><display>(l)</display>submit a written annual report to the:<subsection ssid="1-null-39" dnum="i-o" numlevel="1" lineno=